{
  "stem": "23410.6",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But if you were the second year of-- of university, you-- you had the right to finish the university.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But if you start university, no.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So at this time, I knew about this law.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I asked the same people, in the Jewish agency, to give us the same-- the same if you are a third-year student, forget about it.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But if you were first two years-- and I was only the first year.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] And they collected us all to go.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I said, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Why?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I said, why?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You have for your people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You have nobody.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We-- our students have parents and so on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I said, because we have nobody, we should be worse off than you people?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So, but you cannot compare yourself to us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I came to the meeting [INAUDIBLE] in was at the newspaper [INAUDIBLE] and said, oh, no.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We are not the same as you are.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we are not going to be the same.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this why I broke off over there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They even put it in [INAUDIBLE] and ever since.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And even the-- one of the-- the head of the chemical, University of Jerusalem, the chemical department, is that he was with me but he had already signed.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I said, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And this when I broke off for what they said, I applied to every place else, not to them.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right after the war, maybe '47, '46-- end of '46, '47, I was just in Germany, Munich.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] A friend of ours that was with me in the death brigade, one of the eight people that survived, saw him on a street car in Munich.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And he jumped on him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they started to fight.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they were both arrested.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
